# X (Twitter) Post – Day 02

## Summary:
Today’s post discusses BubuVerse’s economic design, emphasizing how the system rewards active players through in-game mechanisms like Starlight Energy, guild missions, and progression. This approach ensures that players, not just early investors, benefit from long-term engagement.

